[{"_1":2},"llms/index",{"_3":4},"data","# Docs\n\n- [Voltus SDK Documentation](/docs): Build powerful integrations with the Voltus SDK.\n\n- **Getting Started**\n- [Installation](/docs/getting-started/installation): Install the Voltus SDK in your project using your preferred package manager.\n- [Quick Start](/docs/getting-started/quickstart): Make your first API call with the Voltus SDK in under 5 minutes.\n- [Project Structure](/docs/getting-started/project-structure): Recommended project structure for organizing your Voltus SDK integration.\n\n- **Core Concepts**\n- [Authentication](/docs/core-concepts/authentication): Learn how to authenticate with the Voltus API using API keys and OAuth tokens.\n- [Configuration](/docs/core-concepts/configuration): Customize the Voltus SDK behavior with comprehensive configuration options.\n- [Error Handling](/docs/core-concepts/error-handling): Gracefully handle errors and edge cases in your Voltus SDK integration.\n\n- **API Reference**\n- [Client Reference](/docs/api-reference/client): Complete API reference for the VoltusClient class and its methods.\n- [REST Endpoints](/docs/api-reference/endpoints): Complete list of REST API endpoints available through the Voltus SDK.\n- [Webhooks](/docs/api-reference/webhooks): Receive real-time notifications when events occur in your Voltus account.\n\n- **Guides**\n- [Data Fetching](/docs/guides/data-fetching): Patterns and best practices for fetching data efficiently with the Voltus SDK.\n- [Pagination](/docs/guides/pagination): Navigate through large datasets with offset-based and cursor-based pagination.\n- [Rate Limiting](/docs/guides/rate-limiting): Understand and work within the Voltus API rate limits.\n\n- **Resources**\n- [Changelog](/docs/changelog): What's new and improved in every release of the Voltus SDK.\n- [FAQ](/docs/faq): Frequently asked questions about the Voltus SDK."]
